snippet.title: Free Winter Update - Planet Coaster
snippet.description:
Celebrate the holidays in Planet Coaster with the free Winter Update. Play Planet Coaster with this new content update and unleash your creativity with new rides, winter themed décor, plus added management features!

For more news and information about Planet Coaster:

Website: https://planetcoaster.com/
Forums: https://forums.planetcoaster.com/
Facebook: https://facebook.com/PlanetCoaster
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlanetCoaster
